Class MovableTetrisPiece

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.MovableTetrisPiece

  • public final class MovableTetrisPiece

extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a TetrisPiece with a position and a rotation. A MovableTetrisPiece is immutable.
    Version:
    Autumn 2016
    Author:
    TCSS 305 Instructors
